Package org.neo4j.internal.kernel.api.procs

Class Neo4jTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.internal.kernel.api.procs.Neo4jTypes
  • public final class Neo4jTypes
extends Object
    See also type_system.txt in the cypher code base, this is a mapping of that type system definition down to this level. Ideally this becomes canonical. This should also move to replace the specialized type handling in packstream, or be tied to it in some way to ensure a strict mapping.
